Package: EvolPackage
Title: Simple simulation and data analysis code to teach evolutionary processes and macroevolution
Version: 0.0.0.5000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Matheus", "Januario", email="januarioml.eco@gmail.com", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "000-0002-6480-7095")),
      person("Jennifer", "Auler", email="auler.jennifer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
